{
  "stem": "2097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In 1941, when was the Passover coming, was new-- matzah-- was not allowed to have-- to make matzah, there was no matzah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my grandmother's house, the whole family came together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they have an oven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And over there, we rolled the matzah, and we made matzah for Passover.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was in Marghita?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Marghita.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was very close to Marghita, and to my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I should say that I know the same, the area of Marghita and the city-- I mean the little town-- as Simleu, my city, because every summer I was there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, I had more freedom in the summer on vacation, as I had during the school year, at home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 1942-- I have to go there, because this is my hardest years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father, with other Jews-- he was in-- 39 years old-- 1942-- 39 years old, yes-- 39, 40.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was drafted to the forced labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took away about, everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were taken to forced labor, to [NON-ENGLISH] first, and then from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on foot, they were taken all the way to the Russia-- to Russia-- no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the last time when I saw my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He loved me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brunette, tall, and very kind with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the only child, until I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, everybody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was drafted-- drafted from between the age of 18 to 55.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was so, so hard, that the-- the Hungarians-- they knew what they want to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By taking all the man who would be able to do a resistance, or to do something, they were taken away before-- much, much, before.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know what happening, at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
